# to the asset root the renderers resolve against (crab-world/assets); ignore it by
# name anywhere so it can never be committed, including the old repo-root ./assets
# spot a dev may still have. The committed CC0 control glyphs under
# crab-world/assets/controls/ stay tracked (different name).
